data.description: This STUNNING home in MERIDIAN ISD is turn-key and ready to call it your own!!! This home includes 3 good-sized bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and an awesome floor plan that makes this home feel spacious yet cozy! Throughout the home there is beautiful flooring, a gorgeous fireplace and tons of natural light in each space. The master bathroom features a large soaking tub, his and her vanities and much more. The backyard features a HUGE  patio area and there is plenty of room to roam among the area inside the privacy fence. Come see what all this home has to offer and check out the extra lot in a GREAT established neighborhood in Meridian, TX!
